node.text:
Happy 32nd BDAY CB
Us team breezy wanted to take the time to show you how much we appreciate you. Your our idol, inspiration, & role model. You’ve changed our life in so many ways words can’t explain. We’re truly grateful BEYOND grateful to be apart of this amazing fan base called TEAM BREEZY. Us seeing you overcome so many obstacles over the years was very inspiring & uplifting. You’ve made an big impact on numerous of people. The love we have for you is unconditional & will never change. We will always support you forever & always. The affect you have on us is beyond crazy but in a good way. Your motivational words, & music takes us to a different dimension it’s like we’re stuck like gorilla glue haha! Your work skills is phenomenal it’s like you were born for this. On top of this your funny ash, multitalented,& reckless. You’ve been the GOAT since you were 15 now your 32 it’s still crazy to me! But once again we want to take the time too wish you an amazing happy birthday love TEAM BREEZY❤️
